 Trap]]'' (1961)\n| ''[[Two Times Lotte]]'' (1950, West Germany)\n| The novel ''[[Lottie and Lisa]]'' ([[Erich K\u00e4stner]])\n|-\n| ''[[People Will Talk]]'' (1951)\n| ''[[Doctor Praetorius (film)|Doctor Praetorius]]'' (1950, West Germany)\n| The play ''Frauenarzt Dr. med. Hiob Pr\u00e4torius'' ([[Curt Goetz]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Pledge (film)|The Pledge]]'' (2001)\n| ''[[It Happened in Broad Daylight]]'' (1958, Switzerland)\n| The novella ''[[The Pledge: Requiem for the Detective Novel]]'' ([[Friedrich D\u00fcrrenmatt]])\n|-\n| ''[[Premiere (1938 film)|Premiere]]'' (1938)\n| ''[[Premiere (1937 film)|Premiere]]'' (1937, Austria)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Prince of Arcadia]]'' (1933)\n| ''[[The Prince of Arcadia]]'' (1932)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Private Affairs of Bel Ami]]'' (1947)\n| ''[[Bel Ami (1939 film)|Bel Ami]]'' (1939)\n| The novel ''[[Bel Ami]]'' ([[Guy de Maupassant]])\n|-\n| ''[[Ripley's Game (film)|Ripley's Game]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[The American Friend|Der amerikanische Freund]]'' (1977, West Germany)\n| The novel ''[[Ripley's Game]]'' ([[Patricia Highsmith]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Road Within]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[Vincent Wants to Sea]]'' (2010)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Secret of the Blue Room]]'' (1933)\n| ''[[Secret of the Blue Room (1932 film)|Secret of the Blue Room]]'' (1932)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Smiling Lieutenant]]'' (1931)\n| ''[[A Waltz Dream (film)|A Waltz Dream]]'' (1925)\n| The operetta ''[[Ein Walzertraum]]'' ([[Oscar Straus (composer)|Oscar Straus]], {{Interlanguage link multi|Leopold Jacobson|de}}, {{Interlanguage link multi|Felix D\u00f6rmann|de}})\n|-\n| ''[[The Soldier and the Lady]]'' (1937)\n| ''[[The Czar's Courier]]'' (1936)\n| The novel ''[[Michael Strogoff]]'' ([[Jules Verne]])\n|-\n| ''[[A Song to Remember]]'' (1945)\n| ''Abschiedswalzer'' (1934)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Song You Gave Me]]'' (1933)\n| ''[[The Song Is Ended]]'' (1930)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Sound of Music (film)|The Sound of Music]]'' (1965)\n| ''[[The Trapp Family|Die Trapp-Familie]]'' (1956, West Germany)\n| The m